        "brief_description":"An interactive where the characters are Shorta's & Loli's.",
        "created":1607436300,
        "description":"<td align=\"left\" class=\"norm\">In this interactive, we can use any characters from any form of literature, movie, or animation. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nWhat is contained in this interactive is: <span class=\"clgreen\">Shorta &amp; Loli</span> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span class=\"cblue\">What is allowed in this interactive are the following:</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Age digression for adults if wanted [Note: Do keep as a separate thing when making chapters]<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Adult x Shorta / Loli<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Inflation / Expansions<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Weight gain<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Lactation / Milking<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Sexual content<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Transformations : For example <div class=\"bquote\"><span class=\"corange\">Food, object, flattenings, etc</span></div><br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Crossovers<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Popping/exploding<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWhat is <i><b>NOT </b></i> allowed:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Scat/Shit<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Watersports/Piss<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Dipars<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Racism<br>\r\n \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Anything TOO offensive.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThank you all for attending the Interaction and hope you enjoy it!<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlso a quick note, please don't do One line sentences or one-word chapters. please flesh it out before posting,</td>",
